README:
Optogenetics functional MRI targeting the dorsal raphe nucleus in the mouse brain. 
ePet-Cre mice expressing either ChR2-YFP or YFP in DRN 5-HT neurons were imaged for either cerebral blood volume or BOLD fMRI at 7T.
